'''疊氮化銫'''是一種[[無機化合物|無機化合物]]，由[[銫|銫]]和[[氮|氮]]構成，屬於[[疊氮酸|疊氮酸]][[盐_(化学)|鹽]]、[[疊氮化合物|疊氮化合物]]，其化學式為CsN<sub>3</sub>。晶體結構為四方結構，和[[鹼金屬|同族]][[疊氮化合物|疊氮化合物]]相似<ref name='疊氮化鉀、疊氮化鋰具有相似結構'/>。在[[加熱|加熱]]或[[紫外線|紫外線]]照射時，它會分解成[[氮氣|氮氣]]和[[金屬|金屬]][[銫|銫]]。<ref>{{cite journal | author1 = Tompkins, F. C. | author2 = Young, D. A. | title = The Photochemical and Thermal Formation of Colour Centres in Potassium Azide Crystals | journal = Proceedings of the Royal Society of London | series = Series A, Mathematical and Physical Sciences | volume = 236 | issue = 1204 | pages = 10–23 | year = 1982 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title = Handbook of inorganic chemicals | url = https://archive.org/details/Handbook_of_Inorganic_Chemistry_Patnaik | author = Pradyot Patnaik | publisher = McGraw-Hill Professional | year = 2003 | isbn = 0070494398 | page = [https://archive.org/details/Handbook_of_Inorganic_Chemistry_Patnaik/page/n772 734] }}</ref>要制備疊氮化銫可將和[[碳酸銫|碳酸銫]]和[[疊氮酸|疊氮酸]]的[[中和反應|中和反應]]製備；或[[胺基銫|-{胺基}-銫]]與[[一氧化二氮|一氧化二氮]]反應而制得；或[[碳酸銫|碳酸銫]]和[[疊氮化鈉|疊氮化鈉]]的[[複分解反應|複分解反應]]製備，反應式如下:
:Cs<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub> + 2HN<sub>3</sub>  → 2CsN<sub>3</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>
:CsNH<sub>2</sub> + N<sub>2</sub>O  → CsN<sub>3</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O
:Cs<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub> + 2NaN<sub>3</sub>  → 2CsN<sub>3</sub> + Na<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>

